title: Silver 4 Jungle LFT
body:
Looking for a silver team to play and learn with. I main jungle and top is my secondary role.  A set schedule of when we play would be pretty sick too. I'm available pretty much anytime. 

**Jungle:**
Nunu, Shyvana, Vi, Warwick, Zac, Evelynn

**Top:**
Jarven, Teemo and Cho Gath

**Champs I'm learning:**
Lee Sin, Rek'Sai, Kennen and Amumu

Add me on league to discuss.

EDIT: I'm also 19 years old.
